\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Money is not the only way that workers are motivated
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Many organizations, especially in the non-profit & public sectors have a
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

mission
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
(some) workers too care about the mission of the organization they work
 with.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Build a model to study this.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Matching on mission 
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

 less need for explicit incentives
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
But, entrenches conservatism/resistance to innovation.
\end_layout

