\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Additional data from random checks.
 How many children, whether anything on the board, whether the teacher was
 talking to the children, and roll call.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
3 basic competency exams.
 Oral exams testing simple math, basic Hindi vocabulary.
 Written exam testing addition, multiplication, ability to construct sentences,
 and reading comprehension.
\end_layout

