\begin_inset Formula $Y_{cst}$
\end_inset

 is outcome in circle 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 in stratum 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $Treatment_{cst}$
\end_inset

 is continuous between 0 & 1 representing fraction of treated circle staff
 present in circle 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 in the last quarter of year 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

.
