Duflo et al 2013: Setting
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Study conducted in Gujarat: 5% of India's population but 9% of manufacturing
 employment and 19% of output
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
3 of the 5 most polluted rivers in India are in Gujarat.
 Air pollution dangerous for human health in the cities.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Gujarat Pollution Control Board (GPCB) has a stringent regulatory framework
 for pollution control.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
2 Main instruments to enforce regulations
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Inspections (Duflo et al 2018 next week)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
third-party environmental audits.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
