\begin_layout Itemize
Recruitment happened June - August 2011.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
recruitment sites: 113 schools in 106 localities in 10 target regions received
 job postings.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Job ad provided general description of the job, and a toll-free number and
 email address.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Respondents gave contact info and basic educ and employment history.
 Then, based on where they saw the ad, told the salary and a date/place
 for the interview.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
1,920 individuals registered.
 1,665 by phone, 208 by email, 47 did both.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Experiment 1: Salaries randomly allocated across recruitment sites.
\end_layout

