To estimate impact of social connections on governor 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 of colony 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

's salary
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\log w_{ist}=\beta c_{it}+\theta_{i}+x_{it}^{\prime}\gamma+\tau_{t}+\varepsilon_{ist}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{it}\in\left\{ 0,1\right\} $
\end_inset

 denotes connectedness to the Secretary of State 
